data.value:
This project aims to provide a demo of the SDK of Biometrika's HiScan fingerprint scanner, which allows the acquisition and storage of fingerprint templates. The demo allows you to record the fingerprints of different users, and then allows to do matching to check if a fingerprint received as input is part of the database.
Made by Salvatore Alfio Sambataro, University ID : 1000015834
